      <title><![CDATA[Illegal character 问题]]></title>
      <url>https://wujianping125.github.io/2016/07/25/Illegal-character-%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="问题描述"><a href="#问题描述" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java.net.URISyntaxException: Illegal character in query at index <span class="number">59</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="代码内容"><a href="#代码内容" class="headerlink" title="代码内容"></a>代码内容</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">String url = <span class="string">"http://172.20.204.33:81/ifind/verify2?reqtype=verify_pubkey"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">HttpClient client = <span class="keyword">new</span> DefaultHttpClient();</span><br><span class="line">HttpGet httpget = <span class="keyword">new</span> HttpGet(url);</span><br><span class="line">HttpResponse response = client.execute(httpget);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="出现原因及解决方法"><a href="#出现原因及解决方法" class="headerlink" title="出现原因及解决方法"></a>出现原因及解决方法</h4><pre><code>地址中涉及了特殊字符，如‘｜’‘&amp;’等需要转译问题，所以不能直接用String代替URI来访问。必须采用%0xXX方式来替代特殊字符。
可以先把String转成URL，再能过URL生成URI的方法来解决问题。
</code></pre><h4 id="解决后代码"><a href="#解决后代码" class="headerlink" title="解决后代码"></a>解决后代码</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">String strUrl = <span class="string">"http://172.20.204.33:81/ifind/verify2?reqtype=verify_pubkey"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">URL url = <span class="keyword">new</span> URL(strUrl);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//url.getAuthority()带端口80，url.getHost()不带端口 默认80</span></span><br><span class="line">URI uri = <span class="keyword">new</span> URI(url.getProtocol(), url.getAuthority(), url.getPath(), url.getQuery(), <span class="keyword">null</span>);</span><br><span class="line">HttpClient client = <span class="keyword">new</span> DefaultHttpClient();</span><br><span class="line">HttpGet httpget = <span class="keyword">new</span> HttpGet(uri);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[Elasticsearch记录]]></title>
      <url>https://wujianping125.github.io/2016/06/14/Elasticsearch%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h3><p>Elasticsearch是一个基于Lucene构建的开源分布式搜索服务器。<br>官网：<a href="https://www.elastic.co/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://www.elastic.co/</a><br>优点：<br>    完全支持 Apache Lucene 的接近实时的搜索。<br>    Elasticsearch是分布式的，自动分配的写入机制。<br>    易扩展，容错能力强。</p>
<p>缺点：<br>    不支持事务<br>    无权限管理（shield）</p>
<h3 id="常用插件"><a href="#常用插件" class="headerlink" title="常用插件"></a>常用插件</h3><h4 id="Shield"><a href="#Shield" class="headerlink" title="Shield"></a>Shield</h4><p>Elasticsearch 没有自带的权限控制，需要安装Shield(需要购买，试用一个月过期不影响功能但head首页不能查看) </p>
<p>Shield2.0以上安装<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bin/plugin install license</span><br><span class="line">bin/plugin install shield</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Shield1.X 安装<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bin/plugin install elasticsearch/license/latest</span><br><span class="line">bin/plugin install elasticsearch/shield/latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>启动Elasticsearch后，添加admin用户<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bin/shield/esusers useradd es_admin -r admin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h4 id="head"><a href="#head" class="headerlink" title="head"></a>head</h4><p>一款H5的数据查看客户端。<br>安装<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bin/plugin -install mobz/elasticsearch-head</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>查看地址：<a href="http://localhost:9200/_plugin/head/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:9200/_plugin/head/</a><br>默认浏览器查看、curl命令端口为9200，9300为后台java程序端口。</p>
<h4 id="bigdesk"><a href="#bigdesk" class="headerlink" title="bigdesk"></a>bigdesk</h4><p>状态查看客户端，可以查看当前Elasticsearch性能、cup占用、jvm内存等。<br>安装<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bin/plugin -install lukas-vlcek/bigdesk/2.4.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>查看地址：<a href="http://localhost:9200/_plugin/bigdesk/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:9200/_plugin/bigdesk/</a></p>
<h4 id="ik-analyzer"><a href="#ik-analyzer" class="headerlink" title="ik-analyzer"></a>ik-analyzer</h4><p>常用的中文分词器</p>
<ol>
<li>git clone <a href="https://github.com/medcl/elasticsearch-analysis-ik.git" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/medcl/elasticsearch-analysis-ik.git</a></li>
<li>mvn clean install（前提是配置了maven）。</li>
<li>将target中的elasticsearch-analysis-ik-xxx.jar复制到${esroot}/plugins/ik/。</li>
<li>复制elasticsearch-analysis-ik(git repository)中config目录下ik内容到{esroot}/config<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">index:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  analysis:</span>                   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    analyzer:</span>      </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">      ik:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">          alias:</span> [ik_analyzer]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">          type:</span> org.elasticsearch.index.analysis.IkAnalyzerProvider</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">      ik_max_word:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">          type:</span> ik</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">          use_smart:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">      ik_smart:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">          type:</span> ik</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">          use_smart:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<p>或者<br><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">index.analysis.analyzer.ik.type : <span class="string">"ik"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="常用curl命令"><a href="#常用curl命令" class="headerlink" title="常用curl命令"></a>常用curl命令</h3><h4 id="curl命令"><a href="#curl命令" class="headerlink" title="curl命令"></a>curl命令</h4><p>要在curl后面加 –user 验证用户密码</p>
<ol>
<li><p>查看一条数据：zjgy_paper -&gt; 索引名称， paper -&gt; type</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl --user admin:111111 -XGET <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/zjgy_paper/paper/1'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>删除一条数据</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -XDELETE <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/zjgy_paper/paper/1'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>修改id为1的数据</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -XPUT <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/zjgy_paper/paper/1'</span> <span class="_">-d</span> <span class="string">'</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     "id":"1",</span><br><span class="line">     "title":"test",</span><br><span class="line">     "content":"test content...",</span><br><span class="line">     "date":"2016-05-30"</span><br><span class="line">&#125;'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>保存一条数据 id存在会覆盖该条数据</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -XPOST <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/zjgy_paper/paper'</span> <span class="_">-d</span> <span class="string">'</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     "id":"1",</span><br><span class="line">     "title":"test",</span><br><span class="line">     "content":"test content...",</span><br><span class="line">     "date":"2016-05-30"</span><br><span class="line">&#125;'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>给索引加别名</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -XPOST <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/_aliases'</span> <span class="_">-d</span> <span class="string">'</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        "actions": [</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;"add": &#123;"index": "test", "alias": "alias1"&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        ]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>删除索引别名</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -XPOST <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/_aliases'</span> <span class="_">-d</span> <span class="string">'</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        "actions": [</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;" remove ": &#123;"index": "test", "alias": "alias1"&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        ]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>给索引建mapping，注意：分片数量创建后不能修改</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl --user admin:111111 -XPOST <span class="string">'http://localhost:9200/zjgy_paper'</span> <span class="_">-d</span><span class="string">'&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  "settings":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    "number_of_shards":5</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  "mappings":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    "paper":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      "properties":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        "id":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           "type":"string",</span><br><span class="line">           "index":"not_analyzed",</span><br><span class="line">           "store":"true"</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        "title":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           "type":"string",</span><br><span class="line">           "indexAnalyzer": "ik",</span><br><span class="line">           "searchAnalyzer": "ik"</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        "content":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           "type":"string",</span><br><span class="line">           "indexAnalyzer": "ik",</span><br><span class="line">           "searchAnalyzer": "ik",</span><br><span class="line">           "term_vector": "with_positions_offsets"</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        "date":&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           "type":"string",</span><br><span class="line">           "index":"not_analyzed",</span><br><span class="line">           "store":"true"</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="mapping要点"><a href="#mapping要点" class="headerlink" title="mapping要点"></a>mapping要点</h4><ol>
<li><p>对数据量大的字段进行高亮搜索，建mapping时要加”term_vector”: “with_positions_offsets”</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"content"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">"type"</span>:<span class="string">"string"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">"indexAnalyzer"</span>: <span class="string">"ik"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">"searchAnalyzer"</span>: <span class="string">"ik"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">"term_vector"</span>: <span class="string">"with_positions_offsets"</span></span><br><span class="line">       &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>对某个字段既要分词搜索又要聚合查询，要设raw</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"region"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">"type"</span>:<span class="string">"string"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">"indexAnalyzer"</span>: <span class="string">"ik"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">"searchAnalyzer"</span>: <span class="string">"ik"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">"fields"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="string">"raw"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="string">"type"</span>:<span class="string">"string"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="string">"index"</span>:<span class="string">"not_analyzed"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="string">"store"</span>:<span class="string">"true"</span></span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">           &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[CSV导出工具类]]></title>
      <url>https://wujianping125.github.io/2016/06/13/CSV%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E7%B1%BB/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="CSV导出工具类"><a href="#CSV导出工具类" class="headerlink" title="CSV导出工具类"></a>CSV导出工具类</h2><h3 id="指定路径导出CSV文件"><a href="#指定路径导出CSV文件" class="headerlink" title="指定路径导出CSV文件"></a>指定路径导出CSV文件</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">CSVUtils</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</span><br><span class="line">     * CSV文件生成方法</span><br><span class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> head</span><br><span class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> dataList</span><br><span class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> outPutPath</span><br><span class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> filename</span><br><span class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@return</span></span><br><span class="line">     */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> File <span class="title">createCSVFile</span><span class="params">(List&lt;Object&gt; head, List&lt;List&lt;Object&gt;&gt; dataList,</span><br><span class="line">            String outPutPath, String filename)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        File csvFile = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        BufferedWriter csvWtriter = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            csvFile = <span class="keyword">new</span> File(o